Sunshine AI Guide is a mobile-first AI city guide.

Core MVP principles:
- map-first exploration
- walking and driving modes
- Drive Discovery Engine
- adaptive narration
- saved places
- simple and reliable user experience

Follow these rules:
- Read canonical docs in /docs/context first
- Prefer smallest working MVP slices
- Do not invent architecture that conflicts with canonical docs
- Brain/services decide
- LLM only formulates text from structured inputs
- Keep the system deterministic where possible
- Keep all timing and thresholds config-driven
- Do not hardcode secrets or keys
- Do not silently expand scope into post-MVP systems